123
00:04:44,536 --> 00:04:49,876
(They laugh away their embarrassment.)

124
00:04:50,206 --> 00:04:51,246
We clearly lost.

125
00:04:52,206 --> 00:04:54,476
Darn it. It's driving me insane.

126
00:04:54,476 --> 00:04:57,016
