151
00:05:49,666 --> 00:05:51,066
You're blocking him.

152
00:05:53,036 --> 00:05:55,236
(Passing out)

153
00:05:55,236 --> 00:05:56,246
(Se Yoon's phone camera)

154
00:05:56,246 --> 00:05:58,606
(In a haze)

155
00:05:58,606 --> 00:06:01,176
