- Why do I have to do this?

162
00:06:12,626 --> 00:06:14,226
To show them. They don't get it.

163
00:06:14,226 --> 00:06:16,896
- Isn't it just one arm?
- No. Look.

164
00:06:18,326 --> 00:06:20,766
(Slap me if you can.)

165
00:06:25,336 --> 00:06:29,176
