182
00:07:07,646 --> 00:07:08,716
My endorphin level...

183
00:07:08,716 --> 00:07:10,246
This is exhilarating. I'm drooling.

184
00:07:10,916 --> 00:07:13,156
Let's try it slowly. I'll go slow.

185
00:07:13,156 --> 00:07:14,486
