- See for yourself.

186
00:07:14,486 --> 00:07:16,556
- Do what?
- Try a slower speed.

187
00:07:17,426 --> 00:07:18,486
Like this?

188
00:07:18,686 --> 00:07:19,726
You said...

189
00:07:20,226 --> 00:07:21,256
Like this?

190
00:07:21,256 --> 00:07:24,426
