191
00:07:25,226 --> 00:07:27,536
Jong Min. I was swinging slowly.

192
00:07:27,696 --> 00:07:29,206
I meant for you to test the speed.

193
00:07:29,366 --> 00:07:31,706
There's another one. Sit here.

194
00:07:31,706 --> 00:07:32,706
- What?
- Seon Ho, sit over here.

195
00:07:32,706 --> 00:07:34,006
