200
00:07:41,946 --> 00:07:43,716
- I don't trust you.
- With this...

201
00:07:44,016 --> 00:07:45,746
- You hit the bottle with this.
- That works?

202
00:07:45,746 --> 00:07:46,756
- That's a thing?
- Yes.

203
00:07:46,756 --> 00:07:48,786
It's a sibling trust test.

204
00:07:48,786 --> 00:07:50,886
- You put this here.
- You must trust him.

205
00:07:50,886 --> 00:07:51,926
And I go...

206
00:07:52,596 --> 00:07:53,696
Didn't I do well?

207
00:07:53,696 --> 00:07:55,656
If that happens, that's a success.

208
00:07:56,166 --> 00:07:58,526
If I tried and hit him instead,

209
00:07:58,666 --> 00:08:00,196
- then we get to swap.
- Okay.

210
00:08:00,996 --> 00:08:02,536
Jong Min, sit over here.

211
00:08:02,836 --> 00:08:04,566
- I think he's gone crazy.
- The bottle...

212
00:08:04,566 --> 00:08:05,906
(Se Yoon goes first this time.)

213
00:08:06,236 --> 00:08:09,776
(A bit too much energy to say he's aiming for a bottle.)

214
00:08:09,776 --> 00:08:11,176
Here goes. Stay still.

215
00:08:11,576 --> 00:08:13,516
- I don't trust him at all.
- Don't move.

216
00:08:13,516 --> 00:08:15,276
(0 percent trust)

217
00:08:15,546 --> 00:08:17,216
- There.
- Oh, I'm not hitting downward.

218
00:08:17,516 --> 00:08:19,556
- Keep your eyes closed.
- Okay.

219
00:08:19,616 --> 00:08:21,356
- This is the angle, right?
- Yes.

220
00:08:21,356 --> 00:08:22,726
