221
00:08:22,726 --> 00:08:23,786
I'm scared.

222
00:08:23,786 --> 00:08:26,196
(And fire!)

223
00:08:26,196 --> 00:08:27,226
I'm scared.

224
00:08:27,226 --> 00:08:28,226
(Whack!)

225
00:08:28,226 --> 00:08:30,096
(Joon's phone camera)

226
00:08:30,096 --> 00:08:32,166
(Fainted)

227
00:08:33,296 --> 00:08:36,336
