- You're dead.

230
00:08:42,336 --> 00:08:44,176
- Where did I hit you?
- Here.

231
00:08:44,176 --> 00:08:45,746
(You're dead.)

232
00:08:45,746 --> 00:08:47,076
It's so hot in here. Gosh, it's hot.

233
00:08:47,076 --> 00:08:48,676
(Since Se Yoon failed, they're switching roles.)

234
00:08:48,676 --> 00:08:50,186
- He has no choice but to get hit.
- It's so hot.

235
00:08:50,486 --> 00:08:52,046
