- Close your eyes.

236
00:08:52,486 --> 00:08:53,556
I'll trust you.

237
00:08:54,956 --> 00:08:56,326
- Just don't leave a bruise.
- Close your eyes.

238
00:08:56,326 --> 00:08:57,756
(He's focused with his eyes closed.)

239
00:08:57,756 --> 00:08:58,986
One, two. Here I go.

240
00:08:59,296 --> 00:09:02,926
