241
00:09:04,266 --> 00:09:06,566
(He had no intention of doing it properly in the first place.)

242
00:09:06,566 --> 00:09:08,366
- Did I do well?
- You have to switch roles again.

243
00:09:08,996 --> 00:09:11,766
Gosh. What was that?

244
00:09:11,766 --> 00:09:13,076
