- Should we pretend we're bad at it?

257
00:09:40,796 --> 00:09:41,836
- It's quite far.
- Here.

258
00:09:42,396 --> 00:09:43,766
- Nice.
- Nice.

259
00:09:44,366 --> 00:09:45,506
- Okay. Mine.
- Nice.

260
00:09:45,506 --> 00:09:46,976
All right. Send it over.

261
00:09:47,376 --> 00:09:48,376
- Nice!
- Nice!

262
00:09:48,376 --> 00:09:49,506
