2511
01:26:39,139 --> 01:26:40,639
- You cut it off like this.
- Yes.

2512
01:26:40,879 --> 01:26:42,239
Then, you'll see...

2513
01:26:43,109 --> 01:26:44,709
- the node here.
- Okay.

2514
01:26:44,849 --> 01:26:46,379
You should keep the nodes intact.

2515
01:26:46,379 --> 01:26:47,679
- I see.
- The nodes.

2516
01:26:47,679 --> 01:26:49,819
While harvesting,

2517
01:26:50,219 --> 01:26:51,789
if you cut it off here,

2518
01:26:51,849 --> 01:26:52,859
